  "title": "Quality Assurance Executive (Education Industry) #78601",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Education</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Quality Assurance Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central (near Raffles MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Mon – Fri (8am – 5pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Monitoring and auditing internal processes to ensure alignment with EduTrust and SSG regulations.</li><li>Collecting, analyzing, and interpreting data on student outcomes, satisfaction levels, and key performance indicators.</li><li>Identifying gaps and opportunities for improvement and collaborating with staff to implement effective solutions.</li><li>Maintaining accurate QA documentation and preparing timely reports for management and accreditation bodies.</li><li>Promoting a culture of excellence and continuous improvement across teaching, learning, and operations.</li><li>Other required duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Education, Business, Quality Management, or related discipline.</li><li>Knowledge of EduTrust standards and SSG regulatory frameworks is an added advantage.</li><li>Excellent analytical and communication skills.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply, training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78601 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
